-> routed transfer
-> regulated/filter joints
-> active flow
-> main local carrier reservoir
-> secondary carrier reservoir
-> repeated status/phase processing

This is precisely the BALNEO regime: flow, carrier, reservoir, transformation, stabilization, and status marking.

